Tools for fitting of PSPs

Files
=====

fit.py
------

Contains main fitting routine, fit.fit


psp_shapes.py
-------------

Definition of PSP functions with associated methods.

class PSPShape
--------------

Base class for PSP shapes

class AlphaPSP
--------------

Implementation of a PSP shape for an alpha-shaped psp


Demo Files
==========

The description of each demo file is located in its docstring.
For a first look, demo_fit_psp_series.py is recommended.


